OL,7,FThe will face "significant disruption"
OL,8,Fwhen junior doctors walk out for a
OL,9,Fsecond time on Wednesday over pay and
OL,10,Fworking conditions, the has warned.
OL,12,FA three-day strike will begin at 7am
OL,13,Flasting three days after an identical
OL,14,Fwalkout in January.
OL,16,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,17,Fin Wales decided to ballot members in
OL,18,FAugust with almost 98% voting in
OL,19,Ffavour of industrial action.
