OL,7,FIn an interview with ITV Wales, Dr
OL,8,FPeter Fahey, co-chair of the Welsh BMA
OL,9,Fjunior doctors committee, explained
OL,10,Fwhat the coming week entailed: "Next
OL,11,Fweek we have a 72-hour full walkout of
OL,12,Fjunior doctors in Wales.
OL,14,F"These are doctors from the first day
OL,15,Fthey graduate as a doctor, all the way
OL,16,Fto the last day before becoming a
OL,17,Fconsultant.
