OL,7,F"These are doctors who might be your
OL,8,Ffirst port of call before coming into
OL,9,Fthe hospital, they may be looking
OL,10,Fafter hundreds of patients over night."
OL,12,FJunior doctors want to see their
OL,13,Fstarting pay increase from #13.65 an
OL,14,Fhour to #19 an hour.
OL,16,F"We're hoping we can bring the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to the table with a
OL,18,Fcredible offer that can be the basis
OL,19,Fof discussions for where we move
OL,20,Fforward from this," Dr Fahey added.
