OL,7,FDr Fahey described the offer as "a
OL,8,Ffurther real terms pay cut for our
OL,9,Fmembers. This is absolutely
OL,10,Funacceptable.
OL,12,F"The strength of feeling on the ground
OL,13,Ffor junior doctors is incredibly
OL,14,Fstrong.
OL,16,F"We don't want these strikes to go
OL,17,Fahead, we're happy to call them off if
OL,18,Fa credible offer is placed on the
OL,19,Ftable."
