OL,8,Fwelcomed, but that the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment does not have the budget
OL,10,Favailable to increase the pay deal.
OL,12,F"We are disappointed that junior
OL,13,Fdoctors have decided to take further
OL,14,Findustrial action in Wales, but we
OL,15,Funderstand their strength of feeling
OL,16,Fabout our 5% pay offer," Ms Morgan
OL,17,Fsaid.
