OL,7,F"Our offer is at the limits of the
OL,8,Ffinances available to us and reflects
OL,9,Fthe position reached with the other
OL,10,Fhealth unions."
OL,12,FThe Health Minister said she will
OL,13,Fcontinue to press the UK Government to
OL,14,Fpass on the funding necessary for
OL,15,F"full and fair pay rises" for public
OL,16,Fsector workers.
OL,18,FThe UK Government has previously said
OL,19,Fthat Wales has received a record level
OL,20,Fof funding this year.
