OL,7,FDuring the industrial action in
OL,8,FJanuary 41% per cent of outpatient
OL,9,Fappointments and 61% of operations
OL,10,Fwere postponed across Wales.
OL,12,FWelsh NHS Confederation Director
OL,13,FDarren Hughes said: "It is
OL,14,Fdisappointing that the BMA and
OL,15,Fgovernment have not been able to find
OL,16,Fa solution to the ongoing pay dispute.
